  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5cba86031f76152a.jpg?v=1782526187\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Recently, <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2q8KTqq\">American Tourister</a> helped me host my first Instameet for WWIM15! We had so much fun at <a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/home/la-hm-tom-dixon-showroom-20160719-snap-story.html\">Tom Dixon in Culver City</a> celebrating <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/kindnessiscolorful/\">#KindnessIsColorful</a>. I started off the day by picking up some giant balloons at our local party store. They just barely fit in my car! Then I headed over to Platform LA to get set up.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.platformla.com/\">Platform LA</a> is one of my favorite places to hang out so it was awesome being able to bring a small group of friends together for some lunch from sweetgreen and some fun photo taking. You can check out <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/kindnessiscolorful/\">#KindnessIsColorful</a> on Instagram to see photos from everyone else as well!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13b-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6708e149c812d1ef.jpg?v=1782526191\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13c-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cbee5545a3aed0d3.jpg?v=1782526194\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13d-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6e07b2e27fc767c2.jpg?v=1782526197\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/337e8c196acf4572.jpg?v=1782526199\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>During the Instameet, I set up a Make and Take station with the watercolor resist tags from my <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AmyTanOnAWhim\">On A Whim product line</a> so everyone could try them out and make a cute luggage tag! All we needed to decorate the tags were some <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2j27LU0\">watercolors</a> and a <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iFLtep\">water brush</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13f-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d50c4b699137e154.jpg?v=1782526202\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13g-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/10e01156e15ec7fb.jpg?v=1782526205\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13h-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/40ec00221cabd830.jpg?v=1782526208\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13i-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/953b9864b41a8f3f.jpg?v=1782526211\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13j-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0c1972322e3c1740.jpg?v=1782526214\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13k-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/4ae3c82db0b16590.jpg?v=1782526216\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13l-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9b2486b08c5adc04.jpg?v=1782526220\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"13m-American+Tourister+Instameet+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7